      <akn:section eId="sec_16_4604_05">
        <akn:num>16-4604.05</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Jurisdiction.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-4604_05_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A petition under this subchapter may be filed only in a court that has jurisdiction to make a child-custody determination with respect to the child at issue under §§ 16-4601.01 to 16-4604.02.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-4604_05_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A court of this state has temporary emergency jurisdiction under § 16-4602.04 if the court finds a credible risk of abduction.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
